# Claude Zombies - Nacht der Untoten
#
# Inspired by the original Nacht der Untoten from Call of Duty: World at War.
# Cramped spawn bunker with 4 boarded windows. Two doors lead deeper into
# the map: through the Help room and finally to the Pack-a-Punch back room.

NAME Nacht der Untoten

# Spawns - tight cluster at the south end of the bunker
SPAWN   0 -22
SPAWN   3 -22
SPAWN  -3 -22
SPAWN   0 -25

# --- Spawn-room debris (cramped bunker feel) ---
OBSTACLE -12  1.0 -22    3 2 3
OBSTACLE  12  1.0 -22    3 2 3
OBSTACLE   0  0.8 -14    6 1 2
OBSTACLE  -8  0.8 -32    3 1 6

# --- Help room debris ---
OBSTACLE -10  1.0   2    3 2 3
OBSTACLE  10  1.0   2    3 2 3
OBSTACLE   0  1.5   8    4 3 1

# --- Back room debris ---
OBSTACLE   0  1.0  22    8 2 3
OBSTACLE -16  1.0  18    3 2 4
OBSTACLE  16  1.0  18    3 2 4
OBSTACLE   0  0.6  32   10 1 2
OBSTACLE -22  1.0  32    4 2 3

# --- Wall splitting spawn room from help room (door at centre) ---
WALL -21.5 2.5  -6   37 5 1
WALL  21.5 2.5  -6   37 5 1
DOOR   0   2.5  -6    6 5 1   1000

# --- Wall splitting help room from back room (more expensive door) ---
WALL -21.5 2.5  12   37 5 1
WALL  21.5 2.5  12   37 5 1
DOOR   0   2.5  12    6 5 1   1500

# Windows - all four around the spawn bunker, like the original
WINDOW -16.0  -40.0    0  1   -1
WINDOW  16.0  -40.0    0  1   -1
WINDOW -40.0  -20.0    1  0   -1
WINDOW  40.0  -20.0   -1  0   -1

# Wall buys spread across the three rooms
WALLBUY  -5.0  -39.45    0  1   RIFLE
WALLBUY -39.45 -32.0     1  0   SMG
WALLBUY  39.45  -8.0    -1  0   SHOTGUN
WALLBUY -39.45   8.0     1  0   RIFLE
WALLBUY   0.0   39.45    0 -1   RAYGUN

# Perk machines (one per room cluster)
PERK -18.0 -18.0   SPEED
PERK  18.0 -18.0   DTAP
PERK -18.0   2.0   JUG
PERK  18.0   2.0   STAMIN

# Pack-a-Punch at the far end of the back room
PAP   0  30

# Mystery Box in the help room
MBOX  0   4
